Currently most of the countries in the world are trying their best to acquire nuclear warheads and for those that have already acquired they are trying to improve them for currently the military power of any country in the world is determined by the number of nuclear warheads it has.
Here are the countries with the highest number of nuclear warheads;
1. Russia has a total of 6 257 nuclear warheads.
2. The United States of America has a total of 5 600 nuclear warheads.
3. China has a total of 350 nuclear warheads.
4. France has a total of 250 nuclear warheads.
5. United Kingdom has a total of 225 nuclear warheads.
6. Pakistan has a total of 165 nuclear warheads.
7. India has a total of 160 nuclear warheads.
8. Israel has a total of 90 nuclear warheads.
9. North has a total of 45 nuclear warheads.



